@startuml pontos-variaveis-visao-geral

title Visão geral — Serviços, Pontos Fixos e Pontos Variáveis (Strategy / Template Method)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontStyle bold
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

' ======================================================================
' PONTOS FIXOS — os 6 pontos fixos do framework (interface + impl)
' Presentes em TODAS as instâncias, sem variação de comportamento.
' Alguns (Manifestação, Categorização, Designação, Workflow) delegam a
' decisão de negócio a um Ponto Variável; os demais são 100% fixos.
' ======================================================================
package "br.imd.ufrn.core.service — Pontos Fixos" <<Core - Pontos Fixos>> #E8F4FD {

    interface ManifestationService {
        + create(request): ManifestationResponse
        + findById(id): ManifestationResponse
        + findByProtocolNumber(protocolNumber): ManifestationResponse
        + findAll(pageable): Page<ManifestationResponse>
        + update(id, request): ManifestationResponse
        + delete(id): void
    }
    class ManifestationServiceImpl {
        - anonymizationStrategy: AnonymizationStrategy
        + create(request): ManifestationResponse
        + update(id, request): ManifestationResponse
    }
    note bottom of ManifestationServiceImpl
        Ponto fixo: "Registro de manifestações".
        Delega grau de sigilo ao Ponto Variável
        AnonymizationStrategy.
    end note

    interface ServiceEvaluationService {
        + create(request): ServiceEvaluationResponse
        + findById(id): ServiceEvaluationResponse
        + findByManifestationId(manifestationId): ServiceEvaluationResponse
        + delete(id): void
    }
    class ServiceEvaluationServiceImpl
    note bottom of ServiceEvaluationServiceImpl
        Ponto fixo: "Avaliação de atendimento".
        100% fixo — não delega a nenhum
        Ponto Variável.
    end note

    interface ResponsibleAssignmentService {
        + assign(request): ResponsibleAssignmentResponse
        + findById(id): ResponsibleAssignmentResponse
        + findByManifestationId(manifestationId): ResponsibleAssignmentResponse
        + unassign(manifestationId): void
    }
    class ResponsibleAssignmentServiceImpl
    note bottom of ResponsibleAssignmentServiceImpl
        Ponto fixo: "Designação de responsável"
        (mecanismo manual, POST /v1/assignments).
        100% fixo.
    end note

    interface DesignationService {
        + autoAssign(manifestationId): ResponsibleAssignmentResponse
        + hasConflict(manifestationId, analystId): boolean
    }
    class DesignationServiceImpl {
        - designationStrategy: DesignationStrategy
        - conflictOfInterestStrategy: ConflictOfInterestStrategy
        + autoAssign(manifestationId): ResponsibleAssignmentResponse
        + hasConflict(manifestationId, analystId): boolean
    }
    note bottom of DesignationServiceImpl
        Mecanismo de designação AUTOMÁTICA.
        Delega a regra de atribuição e o critério
        de impedimento aos Pontos Variáveis
        DesignationStrategy e ConflictOfInterestStrategy.
    end note

    interface DecisionRecordService {
        + create(request): DecisionRecordResponse
        + findById(id): DecisionRecordResponse
        + findAllByManifestationId(manifestationId): List<DecisionRecordResponse>
        + delete(id): void
    }
    class DecisionRecordServiceImpl
    note bottom of DecisionRecordServiceImpl
        Ponto fixo: "Registro de decisões e pareceres".
        100% fixo.
    end note

    interface AuditEntryService {
        + create(request): AuditEntryResponse
        + findById(id): AuditEntryResponse
        + findAllByManifestationId(manifestationId, pageable): Page<AuditEntryResponse>
    }
    class AuditEntryServiceImpl
    note bottom of AuditEntryServiceImpl
        Ponto fixo: "Histórico / auditoria".
        Imutável (sem soft delete). 100% fixo.
    end note

    interface ReportService {
        + summary(): ManifestationSummaryReport
        + summaryByPeriod(from, to): ManifestationSummaryReport
    }
    class ReportServiceImpl
    note bottom of ReportServiceImpl
        Ponto fixo: "Geração de relatórios".
        100% fixo.
    end note

    interface CategorizationService {
        + categorize(manifestationId): ManifestationResponse
    }
    class CategorizationServiceImpl {
        - categorizationStrategy: CategorizationStrategy
        + categorize(manifestationId): ManifestationResponse
    }
    note bottom of CategorizationServiceImpl
        Mecanismo de persistência da categorização
        (gancho: ManifestationCreatedEvent).
        Delega o critério de classificação ao
        Ponto Variável CategorizationStrategy.
    end note

    interface WorkflowService {
        + advance(manifestationId): ManifestationResponse
        + appeal(manifestationId): ManifestationResponse
    }
    class WorkflowServiceImpl {
        - workflowTemplate: WorkflowTemplate
        + advance(manifestationId): ManifestationResponse
        + appeal(manifestationId): ManifestationResponse
    }
    note bottom of WorkflowServiceImpl
        Mecanismo fixo de transição/persistência de status.
        Delega a sequência de fases, prazos e regra
        de recurso ao Ponto Variável WorkflowTemplate.
    end note

    ManifestationServiceImpl           ..|> ManifestationService
    ServiceEvaluationServiceImpl       ..|> ServiceEvaluationService
    ResponsibleAssignmentServiceImpl   ..|> ResponsibleAssignmentService
    DesignationServiceImpl             ..|> DesignationService
    DecisionRecordServiceImpl          ..|> DecisionRecordService
    AuditEntryServiceImpl              ..|> AuditEntryService
    ReportServiceImpl                  ..|> ReportService
    CategorizationServiceImpl          ..|> CategorizationService
    WorkflowServiceImpl                ..|> WorkflowService
}

' ======================================================================
' DOMÍNIO — entidades JPA dos pontos fixos (Core)
' ======================================================================
package "br.imd.ufrn.core.domain" <<Core - Domínio>> #EAF2F8 {

    abstract class BaseEntity {
        + id: Long
        + createdAt: LocalDateTime
        + updatedAt: LocalDateTime
        + active: Boolean
    }

    class Manifestation {
        + protocolNumber: String
        + title: String
        + description: String
        + type: String
        + status: ManifestationStatus
        + category: String
        + riskLevel: String
        + affectedRegion: String
        + appealCount: Integer
    }

    class ServiceEvaluation {
        + manifestationId: Long
        + rating: Integer
        + comment: String
    }

    class ResponsibleAssignment {
        + manifestationId: Long
        + responsibleId: Long
        + assignedById: Long
    }

    class DecisionRecord {
        + manifestationId: Long
        + authorId: Long
        + type: DecisionType
        + content: String
    }

    class AuditEntry {
        + id: Long
        + manifestationId: Long
        + actorId: Long
        + action: String
        + description: String
        + occurredAt: LocalDateTime
    }
    note bottom of AuditEntry
        Não estende BaseEntity:
        imutável, sem soft delete.
    end note

    BaseEntity <|-- Manifestation
    BaseEntity <|-- ServiceEvaluation
    BaseEntity <|-- ResponsibleAssignment
    BaseEntity <|-- DecisionRecord
}

' ======================================================================
' PONTOS VARIÁVEIS — contratos definidos pelo Core (interface / abstract)
' ======================================================================
package "br.imd.ufrn.core.anonymization" <<Core - Contrato>> #FDF2E9 {
    interface AnonymizationStrategy {
        + anonymize(context: AnonymizationContext): AnonymizationResult
    }
    class TransparentAnonymizationStrategy {
        + anonymize(context): AnonymizationResult
    }
    note bottom of TransparentAnonymizationStrategy
        Default: não altera título/descrição.
        @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    end note
}

package "br.imd.ufrn.core.categorization" <<Core - Contrato>> #FDF2E9 {
    interface CategorizationStrategy {
        + categorize(context: CategorizationContext): CategorizationResult
    }
    class NoOpCategorizationStrategy {
        + categorize(context): CategorizationResult
    }
    note bottom of NoOpCategorizationStrategy
        Default: category/riskLevel = null.
        @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    end note
}

package "br.imd.ufrn.core.conflict" <<Core - Contrato>> #FDF2E9 {
    interface ConflictOfInterestStrategy {
        + hasConflict(context: ConflictOfInterestContext): boolean
    }
    class NoConflictOfInterestStrategy {
        + hasConflict(context): boolean
    }
    note bottom of NoConflictOfInterestStrategy
        Default: sempre false.
        @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    end note
}

package "br.imd.ufrn.core.designation" <<Core - Contrato>> #FDF2E9 {
    interface DesignationStrategy {
        + resolve(context: DesignationContext): Long
    }
    class ManualDesignationStrategy {
        + resolve(context): Long
    }
    note bottom of ManualDesignationStrategy
        Default: sempre null (designação manual).
        @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    end note
}

package "br.imd.ufrn.core.workflow" <<Core - Contrato>> #FDF2E9 {
    abstract class WorkflowTemplate {
        + {final} advance(manifestation: Manifestation): WorkflowStepResult
        + {final} appeal(manifestation: Manifestation): WorkflowStepResult
        # {abstract} resolveNextStatus(current: ManifestationStatus): ManifestationStatus
        # {abstract} resolveAppealStatus(current: ManifestationStatus): ManifestationStatus
        # {abstract} isAppealAllowed(manifestation: Manifestation): boolean
        # {abstract} deadlineFor(status: ManifestationStatus): Duration
    }
    class DefaultWorkflowTemplate {
        # resolveNextStatus(current): ManifestationStatus
        # resolveAppealStatus(current): ManifestationStatus
        # isAppealAllowed(manifestation): boolean
        # deadlineFor(status): Duration
    }
    note bottom of DefaultWorkflowTemplate
        Default: REGISTERED→IN_REVIEW→RESOLVED.
        Recurso nunca permitido; sem prazo.
        @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    end note
}

' ======================================================================
' INSTÂNCIA 1 — Compliance Corporativo
' ======================================================================
package "backend/instancia-1 (br.imd.ufrn)" <<Instância 1 - Compliance>> #FEF9E7 {
    class ComplianceAnonymizationStrategy {
        + anonymize(context): AnonymizationResult
    }
    class AiCategorizationStrategy {
        + categorize(context): CategorizationResult
    }
    class ComplianceConflictOfInterestStrategy {
        + hasConflict(context): boolean
    }
    note bottom of ComplianceConflictOfInterestStrategy
        Designação e Workflow não são
        sobrescritos — usam os defaults
        do Core (Manual / Default).
    end note

    class AppUser {
        + email: String
        + name: String
        + username: String
        + password: String
        + role: Role
    }
    class Department {
        + name: String
        + acronym: String
    }
    class ManifestationAccusation1 as "ManifestationAccusation" {
        + manifestationId: Long
        + accusedUserId: Long
    }
    BaseEntity <|-- AppUser
    BaseEntity <|-- Department
    BaseEntity <|-- ManifestationAccusation1
    AppUser --> Department : department
}

' ======================================================================
' INSTÂNCIA 2 — Ouvidoria Universitária
' ======================================================================
package "backend/instancia-2 (br.imd.ufrn)" <<Instância 2 - Universidade>> #EAFAF1 {
    class PartialAnonymizationStrategy {
        + anonymize(context): AnonymizationResult
    }
    class UniversityCategorizationStrategy {
        + categorize(context): CategorizationResult
    }
    class SameUnitConflictOfInterestStrategy {
        + hasConflict(context): boolean
    }
    class UniversityWorkflowTemplate {
        # resolveNextStatus(current): ManifestationStatus
        # resolveAppealStatus(current): ManifestationStatus
        # isAppealAllowed(manifestation): boolean
        # deadlineFor(status): Duration
    }
    note bottom of UniversityWorkflowTemplate
        Designação não é sobrescrita —
        usa o default Manual do Core.
    end note

    class AcademicMember {
        + name: String
        + unit: String
    }
    class ManifestationAccusation2 as "ManifestationAccusation" {
        + manifestationId: Long
        + accusedMemberId: Long
    }
    BaseEntity <|-- AcademicMember
    BaseEntity <|-- ManifestationAccusation2
}

' ======================================================================
' INSTÂNCIA 3 — Atendimento Público (LAI)
' ======================================================================
package "backend/instancia-3 (br.imd.ufrn.atendimento)" <<Instância 3 - Atendimento Público>> #F9EBEA {
    class PublicServiceCategorizationStrategy {
        + categorize(context): CategorizationResult
    }
    class LegalConflictStrategy {
        + hasConflict(context): boolean
    }
    class RegionDesignationStrategy {
        + resolve(context): Long
    }
    class PublicServiceWorkflowTemplate {
        # resolveNextStatus(current): ManifestationStatus
        # resolveAppealStatus(current): ManifestationStatus
        # isAppealAllowed(manifestation): boolean
        # deadlineFor(status): Duration
    }
    note bottom of PublicServiceCategorizationStrategy
        Anonimização não é sobrescrita —
        usa o default Transparent do Core.
    end note

    class Analyst {
        + name: String
        + specialty: String
        + region: String
        + email: String
        + passwordHash: String
        + role: AnalystRole
    }
    class LegalImpediment {
        + manifestationId: Long
        + analystId: Long
        + reason: ImpedimentReason
    }
    BaseEntity <|-- Analyst
    BaseEntity <|-- LegalImpediment
    LegalImpediment --> Analyst : analystId (FK)
}

' ======================================================================
' RELAÇÕES — Pontos fixos persistem/consultam as entidades de domínio
' ======================================================================
ManifestationServiceImpl         ..>  Manifestation
ServiceEvaluationServiceImpl     ..>  ServiceEvaluation
ResponsibleAssignmentServiceImpl ..>  ResponsibleAssignment
DecisionRecordServiceImpl        ..>  DecisionRecord
AuditEntryServiceImpl            ..>  AuditEntry
CategorizationServiceImpl        ..>  Manifestation
DesignationServiceImpl           ..>  ResponsibleAssignment
DesignationServiceImpl           ..>  Manifestation
WorkflowServiceImpl              ..>  Manifestation
ReportServiceImpl                ..>  Manifestation

' ======================================================================
' RELAÇÕES — Pontos fixos usam os contratos dos pontos variáveis (dependência)
' ======================================================================
ManifestationServiceImpl   -->  AnonymizationStrategy       : anonymize()
CategorizationServiceImpl  -->  CategorizationStrategy      : categorize()
DesignationServiceImpl     -->  DesignationStrategy         : resolve()
DesignationServiceImpl     -->  ConflictOfInterestStrategy  : hasConflict()
WorkflowServiceImpl        -->  WorkflowTemplate             : advance() / appeal()

' ======================================================================
' RELAÇÕES — Estratégias de conflito/designação consultam dados próprios
' ======================================================================
ComplianceConflictOfInterestStrategy ..>  ManifestationAccusation1 : consulta
SameUnitConflictOfInterestStrategy   ..>  ManifestationAccusation2 : consulta
SameUnitConflictOfInterestStrategy   ..>  AcademicMember           : consulta
LegalConflictStrategy                ..>  LegalImpediment          : consulta
RegionDesignationStrategy            ..>  Analyst                  : consulta

' ======================================================================
' RELAÇÕES — Implementações dos contratos (realização / herança)
' ======================================================================
TransparentAnonymizationStrategy   ..|>  AnonymizationStrategy
ComplianceAnonymizationStrategy    ..|>  AnonymizationStrategy
PartialAnonymizationStrategy       ..|>  AnonymizationStrategy

NoOpCategorizationStrategy         ..|>  CategorizationStrategy
AiCategorizationStrategy           ..|>  CategorizationStrategy
UniversityCategorizationStrategy   ..|>  CategorizationStrategy
PublicServiceCategorizationStrategy ..|> CategorizationStrategy

NoConflictOfInterestStrategy       ..|>  ConflictOfInterestStrategy
ComplianceConflictOfInterestStrategy ..|> ConflictOfInterestStrategy
SameUnitConflictOfInterestStrategy ..|>  ConflictOfInterestStrategy
LegalConflictStrategy              ..|>  ConflictOfInterestStrategy

ManualDesignationStrategy          ..|>  DesignationStrategy
RegionDesignationStrategy          ..|>  DesignationStrategy

DefaultWorkflowTemplate            --|>  WorkflowTemplate
UniversityWorkflowTemplate         --|>  WorkflowTemplate
PublicServiceWorkflowTemplate      --|>  WorkflowTemplate

@enduml
